    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Lexend Deca', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .intro {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            color: transparent;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #CD67F9, #AD60F2, #7F46FC, #486EF5);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            font-family: 'Lexend Deca', sans-serif;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .major-text {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .minor-text {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .button {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #CD67F9, #486EF5);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: auto;
        }
        .footer-text {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .footer-link {
            color: #495057;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="intro">
    <div class="logo" style="position: relative; display: inline-block;">
        <img src="public/assets/rectangle.png" alt="Logo" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
        <span style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); color: white; font-weight: bold; font-size: 3rem;">RCTCheck</span>
    </div>
    <div class="minor-text">
        <h2 class="gradient-text" style="font-size: 2rem; margin: 0;">Check your manuscript reporting quality</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="minor-text">
        <p class="gradient-text" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0;">RCTCheck uses NLP techniques to help you access the compliance of your randomised controlled trial (RCT) manuscript with relevant guidelines.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button" href="login/federated/cilogon" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 15px;">Sign in</a>
</div>
<footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-grid">
        <div style="grid-column: 1 / span 1; grid-row: 1 / span 1;">
            <span class="footer-text">
                See our scientific data paper for further details.
            </span>
            <span class="footer-text">
                Jiang L, Vorland CJ, Ying X, Brown AW, Menke JD, Hong G, Lan M, Mayo-Wilson E, Kilicoglu H.  
                <div>
                    <a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-025-04629-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-link" style="color: #0086A1;">
                        SPIRIT-CONSORT-TM: a corpus for assessing transparency of clinical trial protocol and results publications.
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div>
                    Scientific Data. 2025;12(1):355.
                </div>
            </span>
        </div>
        <div style="grid-column: 2 / span 1; grid-row: 1 / span 1;">
            <span class="footer-text">
                Powered by <a href="https://consort.clowderframework.org/clowder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-link" style="color: #0086A1;">Clowder</a>
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
